{{Weapon}}

== Overview ==
The 'Punisher' class mortar fires high explosive 'Chaos' charges that do damage to a wide area (up to five targets). Like most [[:Category:Weapons (Mortars)|mortars]] it fires at a high angle, making it inaccurate against mobile or small targets, but ideal for concentrated formations.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Punisher can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
